{"tid":498690,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"早餐前做運動成個人特別精神，頭腦特別靈活","createTime":"2017-12-14T05:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T16:19:57.000Z","uid":90370,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8fe7bdaa8406e2de1d7662b3479ca7bd60b79e14","tid":498690,"uid":90370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:05:05.000Z","msg":"我習慣每日早餐前做5-10min運動，係床上做下四肢同背脊既肌肉鍛煉，每個動作做20-25下。做完之後成個人全日都精力充沛，而且頭腦特別清醒、活躍同靈活，幾乎無一刻大腦會有疲倦既感覺。個人認為呢個習慣對每個人既學習同工作裨益甚多"},{"pid":"4b0e33f2671aa4328725ad9307a20b9949607b48","tid":498690,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:06:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e40aaf57ca168fa8cbfe3170ea0fe92a2e4cef2","tid":498690,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:07:25.000Z","msg":"每日番工前都去跑山路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跑完司機黎接我番工時間岩岩好"},{"pid":"62ba4f7472cac8a9e46128d6b23d8c0b9942cbff","tid":498690,"uid":90370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:50:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每日番工前都去跑山路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跑完司機黎接我番工時間岩岩好</blockquote><br />\n跑山路用到既時間比較多。如果果日好忙，好多野要處理既話咁就不如早餐前做5-10min既肌肉鍛煉運動，佔既時間會相對較少"},{"pid":"ce03150b68b9e2a047ad1d5b60798298be8b92da","tid":498690,"uid":87433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:52:21.000Z","msg":"其實唔好空肚食早餐就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a132ba1224957eba373b843e6b2ce7be84f8e918","tid":498690,"uid":90370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:17:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實唔好空肚食早餐就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩原因？"},{"pid":"c7743d08afa54d4d9270ccd8393cf25be638c813","tid":498690,"uid":295452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce03150b68b9e2a047ad1d5b60798298be8b92da","tid":498690,"uid":87433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:52:21.000Z","msg":"其實唔好空肚食早餐就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T16:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}